edia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Swimming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglass also made the team in the 200m individual medley (where she is two-time world champion) and the 200m breaststroke (where she is a two-time world silver medalist).\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9801480596428429, \"rank\": 0.020253978426538706, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was fourth in the 100m free at the last two worlds.\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"World Aquatics' entry listposted Fridayalso has Walsh in the 100m free, joining Torri Huske.\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 512, \"end\": 523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Torri Huske\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Torri_Huske\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At last month's trials, Douglass won the 100m free, followed by Huske and then Walsh.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 550, \"end\": 558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9801480596428429, \"rank\": 0.020253978426538706, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two swimmers make the team per individual event.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Walsh also made her first Olympic team in the 100m butterfly (breaking the world record at trials) and the 50m free.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglass, who like Walsh trains at the University of Virginia, could have had a busy schedule on July 31 had she kept the 100m free.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9801480596428429, \"rank\": 0.020253978426538706, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On that night, the women's 100m free final is scheduled for 8:30 local time.\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's 200m breast semis start at 9:46.\", \"from\": 991, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Douglass can still be part of the women's 4x100m free relay and medley relays without swimming the individual 100m free.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9801480596428429, \"rank\": 0.020253978426538706, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999978765576806, \"rank\": 2.1222190352034195e-06, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"se